HEADWORD: Shoring
<hw>Shor"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of supporting
or strengthening with a prop or shore.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A system of props; props, collectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shorlaceous</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Shorl</ent>⟦br⟧
